Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:58.31,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,为它添上颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:06.86,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,再一次来到我的身边吧
